values:
Ah ha ha ha ha...

This whole 'horny beyond reason' thing was a lot easier when I wasn't surrounded by good looking people. 

Damn I hate being in heat.

>> had that nightmare again. Stupid cats. They're all around me! Why can't there be any dogs at this school?


I'm tired. :\ Teachers suck for not letting you sleep in class.

Does anyone know anything about the karate club? I don't want to join the Kendo club because *that cat* will be there.

Chicks TOTALLY dig puppies. It's like, even though they KNOW I'm a daemon, they're still willing to pet me! It's awesome.

And they're all pretty too! And nice!

Hey Sakuno-chan, you wanna hang out some time?
